        "gg9Bxa_cYv0_text": "People Notice the Difference",
        "ggVB5y_QJGW_text": "<p>- Barbora</p>",
        "gg_bkok-kRn_text": "<p>I cannot stress enough how much has changed: strength, balance, sleep, focus… and the list goes on. I finally did my first pull-ups after years of training, not from more effort, but from better connection. I effortlessly move, stretch, lift. This process is not linear. More like a cycle.</p>",
